OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright
OL,6,Fstart to the evening, however cloud
OL,7,Fwill build from the north with showery
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain reaching the region
OL,9,Fduring the second half of the night.
OL,10,FTurning breezy near coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA damp and cloudy start on
OL,13,FMonday will give way to sunny spells
OL,14,Ffrom mid morning. Continuing to feel
OL,15,Fcool with a risk of an overnight frost
OL,16,Fin rural spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
